t-gig-of-2023-3493099">《Pearl Jam》大幅削减 2023 年首场演出的曲目后，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Pearl-Jam-perform-onstage-at-Madison-Square-Garden-on-September-11-2022-in-New-York-City.-Photo-by-Kevin-MazurGetty-Images-for-PJ.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="珍珠酱" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Pearl-Jam-perform-onstage-at-Madison-Square-Garden-on-September-11-2022-in-New-York-City.-Photo-by-Kevin-MazurGetty-Images-for-PJ.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Pearl-Jam-perform-onstage-at-Madison-Square-Garden-on-September-11-2022-in-New-York-City.-Photo-by-Kevin-MazurGetty-Images-for-PJ-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Pearl-Jam-perform-onstage-at-Madison-Square-Garden-on-September-11-2022-in-New-York-City.-Photo-by-Kevin-MazurGetty-Images-for-PJ-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Pearl-Jam-perform-onstage-at-Madison-Square-Garden-on-September-11-2022-in-New-York-City.-Photo-by-Kevin-MazurGetty-Images-for-PJ-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Pearl-Jam-perform-onstage-at-Madison-Square-Garden-on-September-11-2022-in-New-York-City.-Photo-by-Kevin-MazurGetty-Images-for-PJ-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/Pearl-Jam-perform-onstage-at-Madison-Square-Garden-on-September-11-2022-in-New-York-City.-Photo-by-Kevin-MazurGetty-Images-for-PJ-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pearl-jam">Pearl Jam</a>周四在明尼苏达州举行了 2023 年首场演出，演出了 24 首歌曲，带来不少惊喜。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/pearl-jam-gigaton-review-one-of-the-biggest-rock-bands-of-the-century-return-to-semi-brilliance-2634044">Pearl Jam –“Gigaton”评论：：世界上最大的摇滚乐队之一重返半辉煌</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队将许多已经有一段时间没有现场播出的歌曲带回了歌单。他们自2016年以来首次重新演绎《无足轻重》，也是近五年来第二次出演《爱情船长》。</p><p>他们还以《Indifference》拉开了演出序幕，自 1994 年以来，Pearl Jam 的演出就再没有用这首歌拉开序幕，他们还表演了《I&#39;m Open》和《Sometimes》。</p><p>演出接近尾声时，主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eddie-vedder">艾迪·维德 (Eddie Vedder)</a>翻唱了汤姆·佩蒂 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tom-petty">Tom Petty</a> ) 的《野花》(Wildflowers)，之后乐队其他成员也加入了他的《小镇柜台后面的老妇》 (Elderly Woman Behind The Counter In A Small Town)、《Go》、《疯狂玛丽》 (Crazy Mary) 和《Alive》和“黄色莱德贝特”。</p><p>查看粉丝拍摄的片段和完整的歌单如下： </p><p><iframe title="PEARL JAM *INDIFFERENCE* 将于 2023 年 8 月 31 日在明尼苏达州圣保罗 XCEL ENERGY CENTER 举办音乐会" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Yf8UIPOkwTc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe title="珍珠酱 - 圣保罗 - 2023-08-31- 七点钟" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/a7bEu7FZUE0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>设置列表（通过<em><a href="https://www.setlist.fm/setlist/pearl-jam/2023/xcel-energy-center-st-paul-mn-7ba54a74.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Setlist.fm</a></em> ）：</p><ol><li> <strong>&#39;漠不关心&#39;</strong></li><li> <strong>&#39;系好安全带&#39;</strong></li><li> <strong>&#39;有时&#39;</strong></li><li> <strong>“愿望清单”</strong></li><li> <strong>&#39;黑色的&#39;</strong></li><li> <strong>“赋予飞翔”</strong></li><li> <strong>“注意你的举止”</strong></li><li> <strong>《为什么要走》</strong></li><li> <strong>《七点钟》</strong></li><li> <strong>&#39;双重流向&#39;</strong></li><li> <strong>《千里眼之舞》</strong></li><li> <strong>“我是开放的”</strong></li><li> <strong>“微不足道”</strong></li><li> <strong>&#39;女儿&#39;</strong></li><li> <strong>《超级血狼月》</strong></li><li> <strong>《爱的船长》</strong></li><li> <strong>“爱与信任的状态”</strong></li><li> <strong>&#39;门廊&#39;</strong></li><li> <strong>“野花”</strong></li><li> <strong>《小镇柜台后面的老妇人》</strong></li><li> <strong>&#39;去&#39;</strong></li><li> <strong>《疯狂玛丽》</strong></li><li> <strong>&#39;活&#39;</strong></li><li> <strong>“黄色莱德贝特”</strong></li></ol><p>在其他地方，乐队的吉他手杰夫·阿门特最近更新了乐队的新专辑，称它“还不像一张唱片”。</p><p>吉他手斯通·戈萨德 (Stone Gossard) 在去年 3 月的一次采访中证实，2020 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/pearl-jam-gigaton-review-one-of-the-biggest-rock-bands-of-the-century-return-to-semi-brilliance-2634044">《Gigaton》</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pearl-jam-confirm-they-have-started-working-on-a-new-album-3187089">的后续工作已经开始，</a>此前曾与贾斯汀·比伯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-bieber">Justin Bieber)</a>合作过的安德鲁·瓦特 (Andrew Watt) 将担任这一次的制作团队。</p><p> “很多时候，[完成]一张唱片最困难的部分是弄清楚哪些歌曲会被收录，我们是否需要录制另一首歌，艺术作品是什么，标题是什么等等，”他说。</p><p>然而，他确实说过“九月到来”，乐队将重新集结，并“提出我们目前所处的问题，我们将再次提出这些问题”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pearl-jam-bring-deep-cuts-back-to-setlist-for-first-gig-of-2023-3493099">《Pearl Jam》大幅削减 2023 年首场演出的曲目后，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
